Pat Casey,  He completely changed the sport of bmx with his fearless attitude and complete passion for everything that he did in life. Not only on the bike was he a true champion, but as a father, and a husband. He truly was the most genuine guy. As a young father I would idolize him on so many levels as he would always put his family first and for how calm he could always keep in any situation. Pat was one of a kind and He always had the best vibe no matter what. Before I even rode bikes I watched every video of his in absolute amazement, and then got to form a friendship that I will cherish forever.  Thank you for everything you did and may god watch over your amazing family during this time.  Pat4Ever♾🙏🏼

Cheers to all the rad fathers out there🙌🏼 And happy Father’s Day to the greatest father I could have ever asked for. My dad has done everything in getting me where I am today aswell as teaching me how important It is to do absolutely everything in your power to make your boy smile🤍 I’m forever grateful that my own son has gotten to also experience the love from my hero of a dad.  Let the blessings continue 🫶🏼

Suicide awareness🎗  To anyone that is down, lost, unsure, or just scared to open up about feeling a certain way,  YOU GOT THIS!  Life is full of ups and downs and the main thing we all need to remember is “this to shall pass”. You are not your past and it does not change who you are destined to be. Our time is so fragile and meaningful on this earth and when you feel as though you have nothing left, simply look in the mirror and don’t be afraid to crack a smile and love yourself!  Your special, you are loved, and you are exactly where you need to be because life will keep moving and the smallest amounts of time can change your entire life. We are all “Imperfectly Perfect” and the first step is to admit that and not be afraid to step forward.  Much love to all and remember to always be there for one another because no matter what, we’re all in this life together and might as well use our time in the most meaningful way! 🙏🏼🤍✨
